** Isha Dutta**

## Hello!!

Welcome to my website! I am a student at the University of Illinois at Urbana Champaign, class of 2017. I am majoring in Computer Science. I have an interest in Artificial intelligence, web design and coding algorithms in general. Being a freshman, I am still exploring different avenues in CS to see what interests me most. Feel free to contact me!!
